8
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:26,680
The boxing gym

9
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,440
You two

10
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:29,440
The missing boxers

11
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,760
The bar

12
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:33,320
Some of these don't seem connected

13
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,400
What's on your mind?

14
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,360
I was thinking

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,120
