19
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,200
the killer was hinting at

20
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,760
the crimes they committed

21
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,480
You mean

22
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,680
the state of You Kundee's body

23
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,200
and where the body was found

24
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:54,560
also hint at the crimes he committed?

25
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,440
Team Leader

26
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,800
I agree with Shen Man's view

27
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,240
The bar might have

28
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,360
some connection to this case

29
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,040
And up until now

30
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,560
You Kundee's limbs haven't been found

31
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,760
We couldn't identify the deceased before

32
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:10,040
so we didn't continue

33
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,120
investigating the bar

34
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,680
Go investigate it now

35
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,240
As for Lin Wan

36
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,760
leave her to Mei Dong and Ma Nuo

37
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:19,520
Okay

38
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,680
Is anyone here?

39
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,400
Anyone here?

40
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,560
Hey kid

41
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,480
We are police officers

42
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,800
Who is this?

43
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,400
Have you seen this person?

44
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,280
Never seen him

45
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,360
No

46
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:18,640
Thanks

47
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,200
Let's go over there

48
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,600
Thank you

49
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,320
You two Officers came to find me

50
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,000
