64
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,600
Isn't that a good path for them?

65
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,640
Boxing at Rui Lin is certainly good

66
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,040
but what right do I have

67
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,120
to decide for them?

68
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,080
I hope they see the outside world

69
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,960
