70
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,320
This person

71
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,800
has been to our bar

72
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,160
When did he come?

73
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:04,040
It's been about a week, I guess

74
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,320
Are you sure it's him?

75
