Sat right there

77
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,840
I poured his drink

78
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,280
Hello

79
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,200
He didn't stay long that day

80
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,880
He answered a phone call and left

81
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,720
He was generous with tips

82
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,160
