83
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,400
You just said he left through the back door

84
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:57,960
It's right over there

85
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:00,840
Thanks

86
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:02,720
Thank you

87
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,840
So those boxers who went to Rui Lin

88
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,880
are you still in contact with them?

89
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,320
I heard Ah You mention it

90
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,720
They often send money home.

91
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,920
Where is Coach Xiao Dong?

92
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,320
He went back to his hometown.

93
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,160
Did something happen to him?

94
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,760
No.

95
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,400
That's all for today then.

96
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,520
We understand.

97
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,320
Let's go.

98
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:35,920
Let's go.

99
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:36,920
This way, please.

100
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,160
Give it to me.

101
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,520
Are you okay?

102
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:48,720
Kano.

103
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,760
I've told you everything I know.

104
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,760
I hope you find the killer soon.

105
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,120
Okay.

106
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,400
Goodbye.

107
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,480
Are you all right?

108
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,560
I'm fine.

109
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,320
Get up.

110
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,920
Could it be that someone

111
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,080
asked You Kundee to meet here?

112
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,600
But we haven't found his phone.

113
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,520
So we don't know

114
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,040
who called him.

115
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,640
That's the back door of Zhiyin Bar.

116
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,360
You Kundee was asked out,

117
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,400
and then went missing.

118
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,400
The autopsy didn't find

119
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:33,800
any drugs in his system.

120
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:36,280
So he knew the person who asked him out.

121
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,560
Right.

122
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,840
We need to find the primary crime scene first.

123
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,440
Then see if we can find anything else.

124
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,200
Wait a minute.

125
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,960
Why is it so dark over there?

126
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,080
There isn't even a streetlight.

127
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,320
Let's go.

128
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:56,760
Let's go.

129
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,680
Shen Man.

130
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,160
The dust here has been rubbed off.

131
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:07,840
It's blood.

132
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,320
For specific results,

133
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,040
we have to wait for the DNA test.

134
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,560
Excuse me.

135
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,320
How is it going on your end?

136
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,960
Did you find any clues?

137
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,520
Don't ask.

138
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,200
That Lin Wan is a pro.

139
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,520
She answers whatever we ask,

140
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,720
but doesn't reveal a single flaw.

141
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,280
Is our analysis wrong?

142
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,280
Zhiyin Bar

143
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:53,200
and the bar You Kundee went to before disappearing

144
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,000
have all been checked.

145
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,080
There are no issues.

146
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,640
I just feel something isn't right.

147
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:05,160
But I can't put my finger on it.

148
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,040
Look here.

149
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,600
The boxing gym just closed down.

150
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,560
According to what Lin Wan said earlier,

151
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,960
she doesn't manage the gym's affairs much.

152
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,800
Then she shouldn't have much interaction

153
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,960
with these fighters at the gym.

154
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,320
But this Lulu

155
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,680
is very familiar with Lin Wan's home.

156
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,840
The way she opened the fridge

157
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,280
didn't look like a guest at all.

158
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:33,920
There's one more thing.

159
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,040
I also find it very strange.

160
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,320
Are you okay?

161
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,240
You mean

162
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:49,680
Lin Wan's son

163
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,200
