164
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,400
Yes.

165
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,080
Kano is Lin Wan's biological child.

166
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,400
Lin Wan shouldn't be abusing him.

167
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,720
According to what she said before,

168
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,240
You Kundee was very good to both of them.

169
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,000
Then who is abusing the child?

170
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,240
Lin Wan is lying.

171
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,360
If we work backwards based on

172
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,960
the killer's choice of target,

173
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,080
You Kundee must be a villain.

174
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,680
You Kundee hypocritically

175
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,200
recruited students for free.

176
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,680
It's very likely

177
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,800
it was to satisfy his own

178
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,520
twisted desire to abuse others.

179
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,840
That makes sense.

180
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,720
Seemingly kind,

181
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,120
but actually committing many crimes.

182
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,560
This is the target the killer chose.

183
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,800
But even if You Kundee abused these fighters,

184
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,000
these fighters have no family,

185
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,240
and no one would report him.

186
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:37,240
Why would he fabricate that these fighters

187
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,840
went to Rui Lin for professional matches?

188
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,640
What if those fighters

189
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,200
were abused to death?

190
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,960
Lin Wan discovered You Kundee's secret.

191
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,360
She urgently closed the boxing gym

192
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,960
to protect Lulu and these boxers.

193
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:05,360
Lin Wan was living under someone else's roof with her son.

194
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,600
Even if she knew Ah You abused the boxers,

195
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,000
she couldn't do anything about it.

196
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,000
Unless...

197
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,800
what you just said is true.

198
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,240
Her son was in danger.

199
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,440
Lin Wan can handle us so effortlessly,

200
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,320
she must be connected to the killer.

201
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,080
I'll report to the Team Leader to arrest Lin Wan.

202
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,640
Okay.

203
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:22,720
Wait a minute.

204
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,200
Where's the evidence?

205
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:40,320
Those were just your speculations.

206
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,720
The protest issue was just suppressed.

207
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,840
If we have no evidence right now

208
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,920
and you go arrest someone,

209
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,720
are you kidding me?

210
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,240
I found bloodstains in the alley behind the bar.

211
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,280
We detected

212
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,440
You Kundee's DNA.

213
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,360
The owner of Zhiyin Bar

214
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,840
has another bar on Ancient Temple Street

215
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,720
that only opens on weekends.

216
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:15,480
Manman.

217
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:17,840
Manman.

218
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,080
Shen Man.

219
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,040
Team Leader.

220
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,120
Colleagues from all departments

221
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,440
are checking the whereabouts of the boxers,

222
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,960
but there is no news.

223
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:47,480
They can't have just vanished into thin air.

224
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:51,360
Based on the clues we have now,

225
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,960
we still need to start with You Kundee's disappearance.

226
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,560
Combined with Pa Xin's

227
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,880
DNA test results,

228
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,160
You Kundee was in the back alley of the bar street

229
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,560
when he was knocked down and taken away.

230
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,400
Asking You Kundee to meet

231
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:03,560
might have been a trap.

232
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,960
If all this is related to Lin Wan,

233
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:08,560
could it be that Lin Wan worked with the killer

234
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,960
to lure You Kundee out?

235
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,680
He used to be a boxer.

236
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,240
It certainly wouldn't be easy to take him down.

237
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,160
Unless...

238
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,000
it was someone he knew.

239
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,080
Could it be

240
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:25,560
Coach Xiao Dong

241
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,960
participated in Lin Wan's plan?

242
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:29,960
Coach Xiao Dong can be ruled out as a suspect.

243
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:32,720
Because on the day You Kundee went missing,

244
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:33,680
and at the time of the crime,

245
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,560
he had an alibi.

246
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:37,200
Right.

247
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:39,080
Just as Lin Wan said,

248
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,280
he is in his hometown right now.

249
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:43,480
Then could it be that

250
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:45,200
Lin Wan and the killer

251
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,960
used the boss hosting the matches

252
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,680
to lure You Kundee out?

253
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:51,280
In any case,

254
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,720
we must find the evidence ASAP

255
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:55,440
that Lin Wan made a wish to the killer.

256
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:57,320
Otherwise, she won't confess.

257
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,040
Yes.

258
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:06,360
What's wrong with you?

259
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,320
What is it?

260
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:10,960
Are you sick?

261
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:16,720
You don't have a fever.

262
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:18,680
I'm fine.

263
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,720
I probably just didn't rest well.

264
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,080
Found them.

265
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,720
The bosses who often work with You Kundee.

266
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:26,480
There are two of them.

267
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,240
Let's split up.

268
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:37,680
Police.

269
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,600
I need to ask you some questions.

270
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,360
When was the last time

271
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:41,320
you met with You Kundee?

272
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:41,920
No...

273
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:42,760
I don't remember.

274
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,680
Then have you had any contact with him recently?

275
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:51,600
Hello.

276
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,160
Stop!
